ide swath of the room, too, thanks to the extra wide-angle lens.","If you travel a lot for work and want to keep in touch with your baby back home, this monitor is a great option. This device allows you to talk to your baby using Skype while you are away, or you can communicate with the baby using a two-way talk feature when you&#39;re home."]},"id":"2d7fbed0-7c1c-420c-80c7-2fc1d3616781","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Functionality"},"id":"780d4ea9-5491-4adc-95e5-401aeacf4dce","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/X9MQdDuuNdkkRvYAjGQKkk.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The DXR Touch video baby monitor offers voice-operated exchange (VOX) mode, so it shuts off when there is no sound and reactivates when the baby starts to fuss. You can also opt to switch off the screen altogether, regardless of sound levels, and just use the audio cues from the monitor. You have full control over brightness and volume levels, so you can determine the best settings for keeping an eye on your baby.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/56493-mobicam-d-series17.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X9MQdDuuNdkkRvYAjGQKkk.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"X9MQdDuuNdkkRvYAjGQKkk","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/X9MQdDuuNdkkRvYAjGQKkk.jpg","alt":""},"id":"b4f6b00c-d570-4bf8-be73-92591eee801e","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Like other top-rated baby video monitors, the DXR Touch has two-way talk and four lullabies to choose from, with adjustable volume for both features. Both of these features serve to soothe your baby. If you&#39;re on the way to the nursery, you can talk to the baby all of the way there. The lullabies help the baby fall asleep and feel more comfortable."]},"id":"41ad8547-1b70-4cae-beec-fefd19b4655e","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Extras"},"id":"ef203633-2957-4ddf-9998-817d75b4dd04","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/XxASr7JyED6vP5xTHJ4aii.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":